Precious Chikwendu Fani-Kayode (amụrụ na 25 Mee 1989) bụ onye na-eme asọmpi ịma mma site na Etti-Nanka, Anambra State
Ọ bụ onye na-ese onyinyo na onye na-eme ihe nkiri Nollywood.
Precious bụ nwa nke abụọ n'ezinụlọ nwere ụmụ asaa
Ọ gụrụ akwụkwọ praịmarị na Makurdi International School, Benue State
Ọ gara ECWA Secondary School, North Bank Makurdi, Benue State maka ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị ya.
Ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ na Mahadum Calabar, Cross River State, ebe ọ nwetara nzere Bachelor of Science (BSc) na Environmental Science (Forestry and Wildlife Conservation).
Precious malitere ime ihe ngosi n'afọ 2006, na-ekere òkè na SHOWZ na Calabar
N'otu afọ ahụ, o sonyere n'ọtụtụ ejiji na ihe ngosi gụnyere NIGERIA TELEVISION FASHION SHOW, CATWALK FOR CHANGE na GALAXY TELEVision FASHIÓN WEEK.
N'afọ 2007, Precious pụtara onye nke abụọ na asọmpi Prettiest Girl Nigeria ma sonye na Miss Earth Nigeria Pageant, ebe ọ mechara na Top 10.
N'afọ 2010, ọ bụ onye asọmpi na Miss Nigeria 2010, nke emere na Abuja.
Precious, n'oge na-adịbeghị anya, bụ ihu nke ụdị na ihe omume dị ka Face of Safari na Face of Genisms
O meela ọtụtụ mgbasa ozi TV, ọkachasị Medik55 na Passions Energy Drink, nke Orange Drugs Pharmaceuticals.
Ọ malitere ime ihe nkiri n'afọ 2007
Na mgbakwunye na ọrụ ime ihe nkiri ya, tupu ya enwee mmeri n'ụwa, ọ rụrụ ọrụ na Star Advantage Company Calabar dị ka onye njikwa azụmahịa.
A họpụtara Precious Chikwendu Fani-Kayode n'ịntanetị ka ọ nọchite anya Naịjirịa na Miss United Nations Pageants na Jamaica, ọ meriri n'asọmpi ụwa na June 2014.
Ọ bụ onye guzobere na C.E.O nke Glowria Snow Fashion House.
Precious Chikwendu Fani-Kayode lụrụ Maazị Femi Fani- Kayode
Ha nwere nwa nwoke aha ya bụ Joshua, Olufemi, Emmanuel, Lotanna Aragorn Fani-Kayode. Na Mee 25, 2018 Precious Chikwendu Fani-Kayode mụrụ ụmụ atọ (ụmụ nwoke) na DIFF Hospital.
